Reference

Flexio Interaction

Interaction with the Flexio API

getFlexioRessource()

Returns a dataset containing ressources records from Flexio

postFlexioRessource()

Sends a ressource to Flexio. Adds each entry of the given dataset to the Flexio ressource

getFlexioRecord()

Returns a 1 entry dataset containing a single ressource record from Flexio

putFlexioRecord()

Updates a ressource record from Flexio (all the fields)

patchFlexioRecord()

Updates a ressource record from Flexio (only the given fields)

deleteFlexioRecord()

Deletes a ressource record from Flexio

getFlexioRessourceFieldsTypes()

Returns a list containing the Flexio ressource fields names and their types

getFlexioRessourceSchema()

Returns the raw schema of a flexio ressource

Data formatting

setFieldNames()

Replaces the fields names with the given ones

castStringToNum()

Convert a dataset's columns from string to numeric

castDATETIMEToTime()

Convert a dataset's columns from DATETIME string format to numeric

castDATEToTime()

Convert a dataset's columns from DATE string format to numeric

castTIMEToTime()

Converts a dataset's columns from TIME string format to numeric

Data preparation

splitDataset()

Genrerates a training and a validation dataset with a given separation

cleanDataset()

Clean a dataset. Remove all rows containing missing values

Others

saveDatasetToFile()

Saves a dataset in a .csv file
